# API

## pkgDir(cwd?)

Returns a `Promise` for either the top most project root path or `undefined` if it couldn't be found.

## pkgDir.sync(cwd?)

Returns the top most project root path or `undefined` if it couldn't be found.

### cwd

Type: `string`<br>
Default: `process.cwd()`

Directory to start from.
